HEADWORD: Anaplasty
<hw>An`a*plas`ty</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ again
+ <?/ to form: cf. F. <ets>anaplastie</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Surg.)</fld>
